1. dumu nun-e |AB×A| kug-ta e₃#-a ba-zal-zal si i₃-[...]
#lem: dumu[child]; nun[prince]; AB×A[bathing chamber]; kug[pure]; e[leave]; zal[pass time]; si[horn]; X
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. kur me sikil eš₃ abzu šag₄ X X daŋal kur me# [...]
#lem: kur[mountain(s)]; me[Being]; sikil[purify]; eš[shrine]; Eʾabzu[1]; šag[heart]; X; X; daŋal[wide]; kur[mountain(s)]; me[Being]; X
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. ki-ur₃ mah dur₂# [... ...] daŋal#-la [...]
#lem: kiʾur[foundation]; mah[great]; dur[buttocks]; X; X; daŋal[wide]; X
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. ambar-ta me-lem₄# huš# tum₃# muš₃# ni₂# [... ...]-ge-en
#lem: ambar[reed-bed]; melim[frightening splendor]; huš[reddish]; tum[bring]; muš[face]; ni[fear]; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=4

